
@startuml

' Define classes with their attributes and relationships

class University {
    +String name
    +Faculty[] faculties
}

class Faculty {
    +String name
    +Institute[] institutes
    +Employee dean
}

class Institute {
    +String name
    +Address address
}

class Address {
    +String street
    +String city
    +String postalCode
}

class Employee {
    +String socialSecurityNumber
    +String name
    +String email
    +int totalEmployees
}

abstract class Staff {
}

class ResearchStaff extends Staff {
}

class AdministrativeStaff extends Staff {
}

class ResearchAssistant {
    +String fieldOfResearch
    +Institute[] assignedInstitutes
}

class Project {
    +String name
    +Date startDate
    +Date endDate
    +int hoursInvolved
}

class Lecturer {
    +Course[] coursesTaught
}

class Course {
    +String id
    +String name
    +int weeklyDuration
}

' Relationships

University "1" *-- "many" Faculty : has
Faculty "1" *-- "many" Institute : has
Faculty "1" o-- "1" Employee : has dean
Institute "1" *-- "many" ResearchAssistant : assigns

Employee "1" ^-- "many" ResearchAssistant : is employee
Employee "1" ^-- "many" AdministrativeStaff : is employee
Employee "1" ^-- "many" ResearchStaff : is employee
ResearchStaff "1" ^-- "many" ResearchAssistant : is research staff

ResearchAssistant "1" *-- "many" Project : participates in
ResearchAssistant "1" o-- "many" Lecturer : can be

Lecturer "1" *-- "many" Course : teaches

@enduml

---

### Explanation:

- **University** contains multiple **Faculties**.
- Each **Faculty** has a **Dean** (an **Employee**) and multiple **Institutes**.
- An **Institute** has an **Address** and may assign **Research Assistants (RAs)**.
- **Employee** is a base class with derived types: **AdministrativeStaff**, **ResearchStaff**, etc.
- A **ResearchAssistant** is an **Employee** and a **ResearchStaff**, and can be a **Lecturer** if they teach **Courses**.
- **Projects** are linked to RAs via the number of hours involved.
- **Courses** are taught by **Lecturers** (which are also RAs).

